WEBVTT

00:12:59.008 --> 00:13:02.352
Pa, ako uzmete dva tela,
spojite ih i okrenete,

00:13:02.376 --> 00:13:04.777
evo ga oktahedron opet,

00:13:04.801 --> 00:13:06.432
prelepa struktura.

00:13:06.456 --> 00:13:08.620
Ako stavite pravo na pod,

00:13:08.644 --> 00:13:09.861
ovo je oktahedron.

00:13:09.885 --> 00:13:12.588
Ovo je grafička struktura oktahedrona.

00:13:13.255 --> 00:13:15.628
I mogu ovako do sutra.

00:13:15.652 --> 00:13:19.179
Možete da nacrtate tri velika kruga
oko oktahedrona,

00:13:19.203 --> 00:13:21.053
i da ih zarotirate,

00:13:21.077 --> 00:13:25.538
i onda su u stvari tri velika
kruga povezana sa oktahedronom.

00:13:25.562 --> 00:13:29.221
I ako uzmem pumpu za bicikl
i prosto ih naduvam,

00:13:29.245 --> 00:13:32.398
možete opet videti da
malo podseća na oktahedron.